_header: Regem regum a maid hath born
_description: A macaronic song of the Nativity — seven quatrains (aaab)

BodAsh189.First Lines:
Regem regum A mayde hath borneTo Sawe mankynde that was
                    forlorne…
BodAsh189.Last Lines:
…þan shalt þou synge welawyebut þou be lyve
                        hec predicta
